<div id="inbox-approvals" class="docs-section">
  <h2>Inbox & Approvals</h2>
  <p>If you're a supervisor or approver, submissions that need your review appear in your Inbox.</p>

  <h3>Accessing Your Inbox</h3>
  <p>Click <strong>Inbox</strong> in the profile dropdown menu. A red badge on the profile icon indicates how many items are waiting for your review.</p>

  <h3>Reviewing Submissions</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Click a submission in the inbox to view its details.</li>
    <li>Review the employee's information and form responses.</li>
    <li>You can download a PDF copy of the submission for your records.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Approve / Deny</h3>
  <div class="docs-card">
    <h4>Approving</h4>
    <p>Click the green <strong>Approve</strong> button. A confirmation dialog will appear. Once approved, the submitter is notified and the form status updates.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="docs-card">
    <h4>Denying</h4>
    <p>Click the red <strong>Deny</strong> button. You'll be prompted to provide a reason for the denial. The submitter will be notified with your feedback.</p>
  </div>
</div>
